### ==========================================
### RESTAURANTS
### ==========================================

### Get All Restaurants
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants

### Get Featured Restaurants
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/featured

### Get Restaurant Details (Replace :id with actual ID)
@restaurantId = put_valid_restaurant_id_here
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}

### Get Restaurant Menu
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/menu

### Get Restaurant Tables
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/tables

### Check Table Availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/tables/available?date=2025-02-01&time=20:00&guests=2

### Get Restaurant Offers
GET {{baseUrl}}/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/offers
